messages.subject: Icky Feelings
messages.msgSnippet: Hi I am new to this site and have been really discouraged because I am not quite there yet with all of you moms.  I am praying and letting go more and more
messages.messageBody:
Hi I am new to this site and have been really discouraged because I am not quite there yet with all of you moms. I am praying and letting go more and more everyday. PTL! But today, when I read Melissa's story on ICKY feelings at the Book Sale. BINGO...there I am. Thanks for sharing. It has blessed me in a real way!
H.U.G.G.s,
